        if (isset($pdf)) {
            $pdf->page_script(function ($pageNumber, $pageCount, $pdf) {
                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");
                $text = " - Halaman $pageNumber dari $pageCount";
                $width = $pdf->get_width();
                $textWidth = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getTextWidth($text, $font, 10);
                $x = ($width - $textWidth) / 2;
                $pdf->text($x, 820, $text, $font, 10);
            });
        }

        if (isset($pdf)) {
            $pdf->page_script(function ($pageNumber, $pageCount, $pdf) {
                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");
                $text = " - Halaman $pageNumber dari $pageCount";
                $width = $pdf->get_width();
                $textWidth = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getTextWidth($text, $font, 10);
                $x = ($width - $textWidth) / 2;
                $pdf->text($x, 820, $text, $font, 10);
            });
        }

        if (isset($pdf)) {
            $pdf->page_script(function ($pageNumber, $pageCount, $pdf) {
                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");
                $text = " - Halaman $pageNumber dari $pageCount";
                $width = $pdf->get_width();

                $x = ($width - $textWidth) / 2;
                $pdf->text($x, 820, $text, $font, 10);
            });

        if (isset($pdf)) {
            $pdf->page_script(function ($pageNumber, $pageCount, $pdf) {
                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");
                $text = " - Halaman $pageNumber dari $pageCount";
                $width = $pdf->get_width();
                $textWidth = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getTextWidth($text, $font, 10);
                $x = ($width - $textWidth) / 2;
                $pdf->text($x, 820, $text, $font, 10);
            });
        }

        if (isset($pdf)) {
            $pdf->page_script(function ($pageNumber, $pageCount, $pdf) {
                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");
                $text = " - Halaman $pageNumber dari $pageCount";
                $width = $pdf->get_width();
                $textWidth = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getTextWidth($text, $font, 10);
                $x = ($width - $textWidth) / 2;
                $pdf->text($x, 820, $text, $font, 10);
            });
        }

        if (isset($pdf)) {
            $pdf->page_script(function ($pageNumber, $pageCount, $pdf) {
                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");
                $text = " - Halaman $pageNumber dari $pageCount";
                $width = $pdf->get_width();
                $textWidth = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getTextWidth($text, $font, 10);
                $x = ($width - $textWidth) / 2;
                $pdf->text($x, 820, $text, $font, 10);
            });
        }

            $pdf->page_script(function ($pageNumber, $pageCount, $pdf) {
                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");
                $text = " - Halaman $pageNumber dari $pageCount";

        if (isset($pdf)) {
            $pdf->page_script(function ($pageNumber, $pageCount, $pdf) {
                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");
                $text = " - Halaman $pageNumber dari $pageCount";
                $width = $pdf->get_width();

                $x = ($width - $textWidth) / 2;
                $pdf->text($x, 820, $text, $font, 10);
            });

                $text = " - Halaman $pageNumber dari $pageCount";

            $pdf->page_script(function ($pageNumber, $pageCount, $pdf) {
                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");

                $x = ($width - $textWidth) / 2;

            $pdf->page_script(function ($pageNumber, $pageCount, $pdf) {
                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");
                $text = " - Halaman $pageNumber dari $pageCount";
                $width = $pdf->get_width();

                $x = ($width - $textWidth) / 2;
                $pdf->text($x, 820, $text, $font, 10);

                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");
                $text = " - Halaman $pageNumber dari $pageCount";

        if (isset($pdf)) {
            $pdf->page_script(function ($pageNumber, $pageCount, $pdf) {
                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");
                $text = " - Halaman $pageNumber dari $pageCount";
                $width = $pdf->get_width();

                $x = ($width - $textWidth) / 2;
                $pdf->text($x, 820, $text, $font, 10);
            });

        if (isset($pdf)) {
            $pdf->page_script(function ($pageNumber, $pageCount, $pdf) {
                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");
                $text = " - Halaman $pageNumber dari $pageCount";
                $width = $pdf->get_width();
                $textWidth = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getTextWidth($text, $font, 10);
                $x = ($width - $textWidth) / 2;
                $pdf->text($x, 820, $text, $font, 10);
            });
        }

                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");
                $text = " - Halaman $pageNumber dari $pageCount";

            $pdf->page_script(function ($pageNumber, $pageCount, $pdf) {
                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");
                $text = " - Halaman $pageNumber dari $pageCount";
                $width = $pdf->get_width();

                $x = ($width - $textWidth) / 2;
                $pdf->text($x, 820, $text, $font, 10);
            });

            $pdf->page_script(function ($pageNumber, $pageCount, $pdf) {
                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");
                $text = " - Halaman $pageNumber dari $pageCount";

            $pdf->page_script(function ($pageNumber, $pageCount, $pdf) {
                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");
                $text = " - Halaman $pageNumber dari $pageCount";

                $x = ($width - $textWidth) / 2;
                $pdf->text($x, 820, $text, $font, 10);

            $pdf->page_script(function ($pageNumber, $pageCount, $pdf) {
                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");
                $text = " - Halaman $pageNumber dari $pageCount";
                $width = $pdf->get_width();

                $x = ($width - $textWidth) / 2;
                $pdf->text($x, 820, $text, $font, 10);
            });

            $pdf->page_script(function ($pageNumber, $pageCount, $pdf) {
                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");
                $text = " - Halaman $pageNumber dari $pageCount";
                $width = $pdf->get_width();

                $x = ($width - $textWidth) / 2;
                $pdf->text($x, 820, $text, $font, 10);
            });

            $pdf->page_script(function ($pageNumber, $pageCount, $pdf) {
                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");
                $text = " - Halaman $pageNumber dari $pageCount";
                $width = $pdf->get_width();

                $x = ($width - $textWidth) / 2;
                $pdf->text($x, 820, $text, $font, 10);

                $text = " - Halaman $pageNumber dari $pageCount";

                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");

        if (isset($pdf)) {
            $pdf->page_script(function ($pageNumber, $pageCount, $pdf) {
                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");
                $text = " - Halaman $pageNumber dari $pageCount";
                $width = $pdf->get_width();
                $textWidth = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getTextWidth($text, $font, 10);
                $x = ($width - $textWidth) / 2;
                $pdf->text($x, 820, $text, $font, 10);
            });
        }

            $pdf->page_script(function ($pageNumber, $pageCount, $pdf) {
                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");
                $text = " - Halaman $pageNumber dari $pageCount";
                $width = $pdf->get_width();

                $x = ($width - $textWidth) / 2;
                $pdf->text($x, 820, $text, $font, 10);
            });

                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");
                $text = " - Halaman $pageNumber dari $pageCount";

                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");

            $pdf->page_script(function ($pageNumber, $pageCount, $pdf) {
                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");
                $text = " - Halaman $pageNumber dari $pageCount";

            $pdf->page_script(function ($pageNumber, $pageCount, $pdf) {
                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");
                $text = " - Halaman $pageNumber dari $pageCount";
                $width = $pdf->get_width();

                $x = ($width - $textWidth) / 2;
                $pdf->text($x, 820, $text, $font, 10);

                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");
                $text = " - Halaman $pageNumber dari $pageCount";

        if (isset($pdf)) {
            $pdf->page_script(function ($pageNumber, $pageCount, $pdf) {
                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");
                $text = " - Halaman $pageNumber dari $pageCount";
                $width = $pdf->get_width();

                $x = ($width - $textWidth) / 2;
                $pdf->text($x, 820, $text, $font, 10);
            });

        if (isset($pdf)) {
            $pdf->page_script(function ($pageNumber, $pageCount, $pdf) {
                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");
                $text = " - Halaman $pageNumber dari $pageCount";
                $width = $pdf->get_width();
                $textWidth = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getTextWidth($text, $font, 10);
                $x = ($width - $textWidth) / 2;
                $pdf->text($x, 820, $text, $font, 10);
            });
        }

    <script type="text/php">
        if (isset($pdf)) {
            $pdf->page_script(function ($pageNumber, $pageCount, $pdf) {
                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");
                $text = " - Halaman $pageNumber dari $pageCount";
                $width = $pdf->get_width();
                $textWidth = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getTextWidth($text, $font, 10);
                $x = ($width - $textWidth) / 2;
                $pdf->text($x, 820, $text, $font, 10);
            });
        }

            $pdf->page_script(function ($pageNumber, $pageCount, $pdf) {
                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");
                $text = " - Halaman $pageNumber dari $pageCount";
                $width = $pdf->get_width();

                $x = ($width - $textWidth) / 2;
                $pdf->text($x, 820, $text, $font, 10);
            });

    <script type="text/php">
        if (isset($pdf)) {
            $pdf->page_script(function ($pageNumber, $pageCount, $pdf) {
                $font = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getFont("Helvetica", "normal");
                $text = " - Halaman $pageNumber dari $pageCount";
                $width = $pdf->get_width();
                $textWidth = $pdf->getFontMetrics()->getTextWidth($text, $font, 10);
                $x = ($width - $textWidth) / 2;
                $pdf->text($x, 820, $text, $font, 10);
            });
        }
    </script></body></html>
